<strong>BIBLIOGRAPHY ENTRY</strong>
<br><br>
Add a bibliography at the end of your essay citing all relevant sources used in your research, regardless of whether they are explicitly mentioned in your writing. When no publication date is provided add the access date.
<br><br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent double-line-spacing">
	&#34;Title of Page.&#34; Title or owner of site. Accessed month day, year. Web address.
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref-hang-indent double-line-spacing">
	&#34;<span class="hover" title="Title of Page">Swim with Whales: An Unforgettable Wildlife Encounter</span>.&#34; 
	<span class="hover" title="Title or owner of site">WDCS International</span>. 
	Accessed <span class="hover" title="Accessed month day, year">January 7, 2057</span>. 
	<span class="hover" title="Web address">http://whales.org/encounters/big_whales</span>.
</blockquote>
